javax.sdp
Interface Key

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Field, Serializable
public interface Key
extends Field

A Key represents the k= field contained within either a MediaDescription or a SessionDescription. Please refer to IETF RFC 2327 for a description of SDP.

Version:
1.0
Author:
deruelle
